<body class="index-page">

<header>
 {% include "navbar.njk" %}
</header>

  <main class="main">
    
    <!-- Photo banner (desktop)/carousel (mobile) -->
    <section id="services-2" class="services-2 section dark-background">
      <!-- Section Title -->
      

      <div class="services-carousel-wrap">
        <div class="container">

            <div class="row">
              
              <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                  <a href="#about">
                  <img src="/assets/img/fmb.png" class="card-img-top">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">{% if page.lang == 'en' %}About + Bibliography{% else %}Acerca de + Bibliografía </br>{% endif %}</h3>
                  </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              

              <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                  <a href="#archives">
                  <img src="/assets/img/scanning.png" class="card-img-top">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Explore Archives + Primary Sources{% else %}Explorar Archivos + Fuentes Primarias{% endif %}</h3>
                  </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            

              <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                  <a href="#exhibits">
                  <img src="/assets/img/reading.png" class="card-img-top">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Browse Exhibits, Publications, and Projects{% else %}Explorar Exposiciones, Publicaciones + Proyectos{% endif %}</h3>
                  </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
              


          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section><!-- /Services 2 Section -->

<!-- About Section -->
    <section  class="about section">

      <div class="content">
        <div id="about" class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <img src="/assets/img/fmb-logo.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 ml-auto">
              <h3 class="content-subtitle text-white opacity-50">{% if page.lang == 'en' %}About{% else %}Acerca{% endif %}</h3>
              <p>
              {% if page.lang == 'en' %}
                Muntú Bantú is a Memory Center for Documentation and Afrodiasporic Materialities located in Quibdó, the capital city
of Chocó, Colombia.
Thank you for visiting our digital archive, where we seek to showcase archives and primary sources important to
the history of the Chocó, the Colombian Pacific region, and the African Diaspora.
Archivo Afro has received financial support from the Mellon Foundation Just Futures Initiative grant N-2009-09221
entitled “Dispossessions in the Americas: the Extraction of Bodies, Land, and Heritage from la Conquista to the
Present”, administered by the University of Pennsylvania and coordinated by Principal Investigator: Tulia G. Falleti. We are also grateful for additional funding received from
the Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council of Canada and from Penn Libraries, the University of
Pennsylvania, the University of New Brunswick, and the University of Michigan.
Thank you to everyone: the Semillero de Jóvenes of Muntú Bantú, María Fernanda Parra, Sergio Mosquera Mosquera,
Daniel Varela Corredor, Claudia Leal, Kelly López-Roldán, Ann Farnsworth-Alvear, Daniel Tubb, Cynthia Heider, Brie Gettleson, and
Andy Janco.
            {% else %}
            Muntú Bantú es un Centro de Memoria, Documentación y Materialidades Afrodiaspóricas en la Ciudad de Quibdó,
en Chocó, Colombia.
Gracias por visitar nuestro archivo digital, donde buscamos visibilizar archivos y fuentes primarias importantes para la
historia del Chocó, del Pacífico Colombiano y de la diaspora Africana.
Archivo Afro ha recibido apoyo financiero de la inciativa “Just Futures” de la Fundación Mellon, beca N-2009-09221
proyecto “Dispossessions in the Americas: the Extraction of Bodies, Land, and Heritage from la Conquista to the
Present” administrada por la Universidad de Pensilvania y coordinada Tulia Falleti. También expresamos nuestra gratitud por el apoyo
recibido del Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council of Canada, Penn Libraries, la Universidad de
Pennsylvania, la Universidad de New Brunswick y la Universidad de Michigan.
Gracias a todes: Las y los del Semillero de Jóvenes de Muntú Bantú, María Fernanda Parra, Sergio Mosquera Mosquera,
Daniel Varela Corredor, Claudia Leal, Kelly López-Roldán, Ann Farnsworth-Alvear, Daniel Tubb, Cynthia Heider, Brie
Gettleson, y Andy Janco.
         {% endif %}
              </p>

              
                
                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section><!-- /About Section -->

    
    <!-- Recent Posts Section -->
    <section id="archives" class="recent-posts section">

      <!-- Section Title -->
      <div class="container section-title" >
        <h2>{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Archives + Primary Sources{% else %}Archivos + Fuentes Primarias{% endif %}</h2>
      </div><!-- End Section Title -->

      <div class="container">

        <div class="row gy-5">
          {%- for archive in collections.archives -%}
          <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="post-item position-relative h-100"  data-aos-delay="100">

              <div class="post-img position-relative overflow-hidden">
                <img src="{{ archive.data.thumbnail }}" class="img-fluid" alt="{{ archive.data.title }}">
                {% if archive.data.date %}
                <span class="post-date">{{ archive.data.date }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>

              <div class="post-content d-flex flex-column">
              <!-- insert the Type if available -->  
             {% if archive.data.type %}
              <div class="pb-3">
                <span class="badge text-white bg-primary">{{ archive.data.type }}</span>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
              <!-- use English language title if available when site is in English mode -->
                {% if page.lang == 'en' %}
                  {% if archive.data.titleEng %}
                  <h3 class="post-title">{{ archive.data.titleEng }}</h3>
                  {% else %}
                  <h3 class="post-title">{{ archive.data.title }}</h3>
                  {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                <h3 class="post-title">{{ archive.data.title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="meta d-flex align-items-center">
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-person"></i> <span class="ps-2">{{ archive.data.author }}</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="px-3 text-black-50">/</span>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-folder2"></i> <span class="ps-2">{{ archive.data.topic }}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <hr>

                <a href="{{ archive.data.link }}" class="readmore stretched-link">
                  <span>{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Read more{% else %}Lee más{% endif %}</span><i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>

              </div>

            </div>
          </div><!-- End post item -->
          {% endfor %}
          
        </div>

      </div>

    </section><!-- /Recent Posts Section -->

    <!-- Recent Posts Section -->
    <section id="exhibits" class="recent-posts section">

      <!-- Section Title -->
      <div class="container section-title" >
        <h2>{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Exhibits, Publications, and Projects{% else %}Exposiciones, Publicaciones + Proyectos{% endif %}</h2>
      </div><!-- End Section Title -->

      <div class="container">

        <div class="row gy-5">
            {%- for exhibit in collections.exhibits -%}

          <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="post-item position-relative h-100"  data-aos-delay="100">

              <div class="post-img position-relative overflow-hidden">
                <img src="{{ exhibit.data.thumbnail }}" class="img-fluid" alt="{{ exhibit.data.title }}">
                <span class="post-date">{{ exhibit.data.date }}</span>
              </div>

              <div class="post-content d-flex flex-column">
                            
              <!-- use English language title if available when site is in English mode -->
                              {% if page.lang == 'en' %}
                  {% if archive.data.titleEng %}
                  <h3 class="post-title">{{ exhibit.data.titleEng }}</h3>
                  {% else %}
                  <h3 class="post-title">{{ exhibit.data.title }}</h3>
                  {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                <h3 class="post-title">{{ exhibit.data.title }}</h3>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="meta d-flex align-items-center">
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-person"></i> <span class="ps-2">{{ exhibit.data.author }}</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="px-3 text-black-50">/</span>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-folder2"></i> <span class="ps-2">{{ exhibit.data.topic }}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <hr>

                <a href="{{ exhibit.data.link }}" class="readmore stretched-link">
                  <span>{% if page.lang == 'en' %}Read more{% else %}Lee más{% endif %}</span><i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>

              </div>

            </div>
          </div><!-- End post item -->
          {% endfor %}
          
        </div>

      </div>

    </section><!-- /Recent Posts Section -->


  </main>

<div id="search-modal" class="modal modal-xl" tabindex="-1">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div id="search" class="search"></div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  {% include 'footer.njk' %}

  <!-- Scroll Top -->
  <a href="#" id="scroll-top" class="scroll-top d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"><i class="bi bi-arrow-up-short"></i></a>

  <!-- Preloader -->
  <div id="preloader"></div>

  <!-- Vendor JS Files -->
  <script src="/assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/vendor/php-email-form/validate.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/vendor/aos/aos.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/vendor/glightbox/js/glightbox.min.js"></script>

  <!-- Main JS File -->
  <script src="/assets/js/main.js"></script>
  <script>
    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
        new PagefindUI({ element: "#search", showSubResults: true });
        let myModal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('search-modal'), {
          keyboard: false
        })
        document.getElementById('search-icon').addEventListener('click', function() {
          myModal.show();
        });

    });
  </script>
  {% block extrajs %}{% endblock %}

</body>

</html>
